{"tid":1434193,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警例記招係政府陰謀！！","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T16:47:17.000Z","uid":271687,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f6fce443fd18a9a7e0b311107b5feffc9509bd1a","tid":1434193,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"黑警日日開記招，大話連編咁反駁問題。<br />\n答唔到問題就話無資料，無數據係手。<br />\n出得嚟開記招，你仲無資料無數據？係咪玩我地香港人啊。<br />\n<br />\n政府就係叫警隊每日開記招，係想等警察大話連編咁洗香港人腦，想分割我地！<br />\n<br />\n我明白有啲人意志堅定唔會咁易被洗腦。<br />\n但另一部分呢？<br />\n<br />\n所以！開記招時，我地嘅記者一定要切佢生豬肉。唔好比佢班警犬係到尻吠！"},{"pid":"f8869cbdcf778dbf856239b32753eef4fe334312","tid":1434193,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64aafbb857b6a8534bfa36d39a886d3c25695625","tid":1434193,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:45:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec64bff40c2e1b50941ea6f8dc7a2b0a5011ce70","tid":1434193,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3e59539367fdfa7a835b81fc21317fc82d5a4d9","tid":1434193,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"推"}]}